:["突然，你发现前面的队伍中，出现了一个格格不入的身影。"]},{"code":241,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"萤雪","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["一个穿着旗袍的少女，在周围的人群中，显得非常突兀。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>欸，那个是，，萤雪吗？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\<n>（这么说起来，人群里面穿旗袍的也就只有她了吧，）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>（没想到那样的大小姐居然也会来买垃圾食品啊，）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["她没有注意到你，一边专注的看着菜单，手指一边轻轻地"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["数着什么。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>，，这是在干什么，是在挑兵挑将吗？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<店长>好了，下一位客人。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["队伍很快到了萤雪，但是她还没有数完，而且肉眼可见地"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["慌张了起来。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<店长>那个，请问选好了吗？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["在用飞快的速度数了一番之后，她露出了放心的微笑。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>我要这个！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["周围的顾客投来好奇和惊讶的目光。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["店长没有多问，很快地把食品交给了萤雪。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["然后你就看到了一边拿着大号冰淇淋，一边露出委屈表情"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["的萤雪。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"cg萤雪买饭",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["接着，就在她准备逃离这里的时候，她对上了你的目光。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["你感觉她浑身都僵住了一秒钟。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"CG萤雪买饭 2",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>那个，请，请不要误会哦。我早上一般都喜欢吃一些冷饮的。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>（你这样一解释不是显得更可怜了吗。。）"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>等我一下哦"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["没过一会，你就拿着两个巨无霸汉堡。来到了萤雪身边。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>这么大一份冰淇淋你肯定吃不完吧。"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["我用我这个和你交换一半吧！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>欸，，没。没事的。哈哈哈，我其实喜欢早上吃冷饮的。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>虽然，它们又冷又凉，吃完还会饥饿。。。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>好了，别客气了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["你强行拉起她的手，把汉堡放上去。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["你感到，她的手颤抖了一下，但是并没有强烈的反抗。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>那就不好意思了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["你朝她摆摆手。转身离去。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>那个，我的冰淇淋还没有给你呢。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<你>奥，你先吃吧，到了教室把剩下的给我就行。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\n<萤雪>什，什么！太变态了！亏我刚才还以为你是君子呢！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"par